
= Installation =

Pull the code:
<pre>
git clone ssh://<username>@git.opendaylight.org:29418/openflowjava.git
</pre>

and import project into your IDE

= Configuration =
Library is started and configured by Openflow Plugin. Library can be started and configured also by itself (via Integration test).

=== Startup in Openflow Plugin (or other component)===
Any component that wants to use the library's funcionality needs to import the library's bundle. To start the library it is needed to:
* 1. configure,
* 2. inject SwitchConnectionHandler,
* 3. start the library

NOTE: detailed description can be found here: [Openflow_Protocol_Library:Openflow_Protocol_Library%27s_lifecycle|Library's lifecycle]
